headline: Bank earnings, Fed comments, jobless claims: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime Host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Thursday, January 15, including earnings results from Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company (TSM), Morgan Stanley (MS), Goldman Sachs (GS), and BlackRock (BLK); commentary from Federal Reserve officials; and the latest reading on initial jobless claims. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.
